    "en": {
      "title": "Ruwan Police Legal Division",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Senior Superintendent of Police Advocate Ruwan Gunasekara has been appointed as the Director of the Police Legal Division with immediate effect, the police headquarters said.",
        "Mr. Ruwan Gunasekara has been working as the Director of Court Security Division before his new position.",
        "The Police Headquarters says that the appointment has been made by the Inspector General of Police subject to the approval of the Secretary of the Ministry of Public Security."
      ],
